data.title: The Deluxtone - Rockets (CD)
data.meta_description: New Factory Sealed 1999 Tooth AND NAIL TND1139 Rockabilly, swing, jump blues, spacy reverb-drenched surf guitar -- the Deluxtone Rockets cover it all on their self-titled debut, but rather than coming off as eclectic fans of the styles they play, they simply sound like they can't decide which trendy retro sound to foll
